:1051,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"ac","roundness":null,"containerId":"TknJ2EoienoKSw09wOD20","originalText":"\nPROTOCOL LENS","height":50,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1981319423,"textAlign":"center","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":1498.6155686896789,"angle":0,"y":455.52604475938415,"width":173.36000061035156},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":["UXSWa__hSZP5LwKBj97y7"],"index":"ae","backgroundColor":"transparent","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":590,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772331520101,"id":"gtph3T_b8WJktbxbNS6Qd","x":1410.3163757697782,"seed":522847135,"boundElements":[{"type":"text","id":"HbNjjXPrF8RFafXm1_chc"}],"y":908.9142192432048,"opacity":100,"height":228.7959451561519,"width":340.44081900252451,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1927902719},{"seed":327563199,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"HbNjjXPrF8RFafXm1_chc","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":17.365588583644886,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"middle","updated":1772331520101,"locked":false,"text":"SUBJECT details","version":693,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"af","roundness":null,"containerId":"gtph3T_b8WJktbxbNS6Qd","originalText":"SUBJECT details","height":21.706985729556109,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":["UXSWa__hSZP5LwKBj97y7"],"versionNonce":2003328543,"textAlign":"center","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":1506.2294274829546,"angle":0,"y":1012.4586989565028,"width":148.61471557617188},{"seed":272042513,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"6SkSSY8mlZamOTy8RQWJp","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":20,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772331817087,"locked":false,"text":"The system needs to be able to show the universal manifest for both sides with a explorable\ncollapsible hierarchy explorer which we should reuse throughout all of this stuff and it needs\nto show the elements like the shards for example that are shareable in different situations so\nthat the universal manifest examples here have a complete set of all the different items that\nare going to be shown in any of the examples. So it would have DIDs and URLs. I can't go\ninto the full list. And then you would be able to see the shard, for example, that's actually\nshared in the protocol handshake or whatever we're calling it. The protocol part on the top\nshows the where it says protocol lens shows the step-by-step interactions And what's\nhappening in the protocol so you can step through it the subject shows the What you're\ncalling an entity I think I just don't want to get the nomenclature wrong here, but the thing\nthat's being talked used to communicate back and forth and the state of it and Then on\neach side the session state shows what each entity thinks or knows about the other and It\nwould go from not knowing there was another entity to getting back the requested info. ","version":463,"autoResize":false,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"ag","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"The system needs to be able to show the universal manifest for both sides with a explorable collapsible hierarchy explorer which we should reuse throughout all of this stuff and it needs to show the elements like the shards for example that are shareable in different situations so that the universal manifest examples here have a complete set of all the different items that are going to be shown in any of the examples. So it would have DIDs and URLs. I can't go into the full list. And then you would be able to see the shard, for example, that's actually shared in the protocol handshake or whatever we're calling it. The protocol part on the top shows the where it says protocol lens shows the step-by-step interactions And what's happening in the protocol so you can step through it the subject shows the What you're calling an entity I think I just don't want to get the nomenclature wrong here, but the thing that's being talked used to communicate back and forth and the state of it and Then on each side the session state shows what each entity thinks or knows about the other and It would go from not knowing there was another entity to getting back the requested info. ","height":325,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":659478303,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":null,"x":916.18834440672777,"angle":0,"y":1274.8217955506711,"width":928.60118626734629},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"ah","backgroundColor":"transparent","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":88,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772331841404,"id":"8EdB3s0918EnKGmZTroXC","x":907.65638710746816,"seed":483923839,"boundElements":[{"type":"text","id":"io3spR-VekmUJ8XebvDrX"}],"y":337.5714747490764,"opacity":100,"height":76.787615693340967,"width":1363.4067764217652,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1716275935},{"seed":1155880113,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"io3spR-VekmUJ8XebvDrX","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":20,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"middle","updated":1772331908500,"locked":false,"text":"  < BACK   [ TITLE ]                                  STEP TRASNSPORT CONTROLS   ","version":117,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"ahV","roundness":null,"containerId":"8EdB3s0918EnKGmZTroXC","originalText":"  < BACK   [ TITLE ]                                  STEP TRASNSPORT CONTROLS   ","height":25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":889898417,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":null,"x":912.65638710746816,"angle":0,"y":363.46528259574688,"width":842.14013671875},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"ak","backgroundColor":"transparent","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":140,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772331941848,"id":"3uhrQc0pFT5LzwapvVkj6","x":1030.5165722168144,"seed":1227164351,"boundElements":null,"y":1786.2978241634428,"opacity":100,"height":348.10385780981233,"width":426.59786496300512,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":527927519},{"seed":521078865,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"iIxixVBQhxfrpj8tQZEN5","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":20,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772331975575,"locked":false,"text":"ENTITY\/SUBJECT DETAILS CARD","version":82,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"al","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"ENTITY\/SUBJECT DETAILS CARD","height":25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1501946847,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":null,"x":1056.1124441145939,"angle":0,"y":1736.812471827734,"width":355.17999267578125},{"seed":1355373631,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"IB_qaj2mkFWNfEyXH9kdn","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":20,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772332306673,"locked":false,"text":"The details card should have two\nmodes. In both modes you're seeing\nthe header for what the details\nare at the top. So it's either the\nentity details or the universal\nmanifest details or the subject\ndetails. \n\nThere should be on all details two\nviews you can toggle between one\nis a human friendly summary using a\ncollapsible hierarchy list and the\nother is the raw structured data\nwith a quality renderer that\nhandles indents properly so it's\neasy to read. Clicking the JSON\nbutton will toggle states. ","version":131,"autoResize":false,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"am","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"The details card should have two modes. In both modes you're seeing the header for what the details are at the top. So it's either the entity details or the universal manifest details or the subject details. \n\nThere should be on all details two views you can toggle between one is a human friendly summary using a collapsible hierarchy list and the other is the raw structured data with a quality renderer that handles indents properly so it's easy to read. Clicking the JSON button will toggle states. ","height":425,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1128193055,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":null,"x":1521.9573126541957,"angle":0,"y":1731.6932974481781,"width":347.47988667054432},{"seed":1428757343,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"5ZmQv_GfyBK_T6qJdO3K5","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":20,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772332267622,"locked":false,"text":"[ DATA TYPE ]","version":129,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"an","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"[ DATA TYPE ]","height":25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":111141745,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":null,"x":1170.4406719246795,"angle":0,"y":1796.5361729225538,"width":155.48001098632812},{"seed":1963147583,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"vUXStTGOPutUJJCMT-WG3","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":20,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772332270104,"locked":false,"text":"[ TITLE ]","version":74,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundCo